    "summary": "The user asks technical automotive diagnostic questions regarding a P0171 lean condition code on a 2018 Camry. The assistant provides accurate mechanical advice but consistently layers it with heavy, unprompted fantasy metaphors involving goblins, gremlins, runes, and quests.",
